data.title: Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture
data.meta_description: The Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Motion Picture (or Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture), is an award given by the Screen Actors Guild to honor the finest acting achievements in film. 1995: Apollo 13...
data.text:
Recently, we've done several changes to help out this wiki, from deleting empty pages, improving the navigation, adding a rules page, as well as merging film infoboxes.

You can check out the latest overhauls that we have done on this wiki so far, as well as upcoming updates in our announcement post here.
